{
  "chapter": 51,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十一回 大难竟不死\n\n风暴过后，梅谦、公孙红、万老夫人在破碎的船舱中幸存。三人被一股神秘力量拉向一座荒岛，一个赤身裸体、形如鬼魅的怪物以一人之力将船拉上岸，轻松击败梅谦与公孙红两大高手。万老夫人被迫扛着食物随怪物深入丛林，却发现这怪物竟是昔日名动天下的伽星大师——他被岁月与饥饿摧残得面目全非，却仍对一个神秘的\"妖精\"言听计从。\n\n荒岛中央藏着一艘残破的大船，五色锦帆在朝阳下升起，水天姬现身。她已在这荒岛上被困七年，美貌未减，却将寂寞寄托于五色锦帆。船舱中还有一个铁制密室，里面关着一个人——正是胡不愁。水天姬每日为他送食，他却只能在密室中修炼。万老夫人以敏锐的洞察力击穿水天姬的心防，逼出了她对胡不愁的真实感情。两个被困荒岛的女子，在寂寞中互相倾诉。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_qian",
      "speaker_name": "梅谦",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "text": "公孙红……公孙红……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "speaker_name": "公孙红",
      "listener": "char_mei_qian",
      "text": "我在这里。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_qian",
      "speaker_name": "梅谦",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "text": "好……公孙红，你还未死。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_qian",
      "speaker_name": "梅谦",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "text": "公孙红。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "speaker_name": "公孙红",
      "listener": "char_mei_qian",
      "text": "是我……万老夫人呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_qian",
      "speaker_name": "梅谦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这……哎哟！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "speaker_name": "公孙红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她……她莫非已……已……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_qian",
      "speaker_name": "梅谦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫她抓紧，谁知她……唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "speaker_name": "公孙红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可怜……不想她竟……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_qian",
      "speaker_name": "梅谦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她虽非好人，但这么大年纪，终年飘泊在外，也可说得上是孤苦伶仃，有些事，别人也该原谅才是。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "speaker_name": "公孙红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她外表虽恶毒，其实心里也必定凄凉痛苦得很，是以行事便难免有些失常，这确是应当原谅她的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "text": "多谢你们说我好话。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "speaker_name": "公孙红",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "是万老夫人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_qian",
      "speaker_name": "梅谦",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "是万老夫人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "text": "正是我老婆子，我还未死。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想我老婆子死了，也有人会为我叹息，早知如此，倒是死了也好。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_qian",
      "speaker_name": "梅谦",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "text": "如何？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "speaker_name": "公孙红",
      "listener": "char_mei_qian",
      "text": "无论他是人是鬼，也得和他拼了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_qian",
      "speaker_name": "梅谦",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "text": "对！先下手为强。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "得手了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "text": "你……你为何不敢吃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我为何不敢吃？只因我要留给那妖精……留给那磨死人的妖精。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "站起来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "text": "你……你要……要我……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我要你站起来。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "text": "我的肉又老又粗，还是……还是这两人年轻力壮，你……你要吃，就……就吃他们两个吧！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你年纪虽大，身子倒也健壮。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "text": "你……你真要……真要……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我要你将那些吃的全拾起来，送给那妖精去。你若运气好，等那妖精吃剩下时，说不定也分给你一份。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妖精……总有一天……到了那一天，我就要将你那一身细皮的肉一寸寸割下来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "到了，就是这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "水天姬！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "想不到……真是想不到，在这荒岛上居然也会遇着故人……万老夫人，瞧！你又发福了，这些年来，你日子过得必定很好。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你只怕也想不到会在这里遇见我吧？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "我，我……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "多年不见，现在你难道除了'我'字，就不会说别的话了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "我这是做梦？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "text": "很好，你果然听话得很，没有偷吃。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "speaker_name": "伽星大师",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "没有偷吃很多，只偷吃了两口。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你不知道，在这荒岛上，日子过得有多苦。能有海鸟飞过，能有鱼蟹上钩，就算是这一天走运了，所以……就连我们大名鼎鼎的一代高僧——伽星大师，若是瞧见了好吃的东西，也忍不住要偷吃了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "伽星大师？他就是伽星大师？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "如假包换，一点不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天呀……天呀！这会是真的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我也但愿不是真的才好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "伽星大师……这会是伽星大师？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "亏得是伽星大师……这些年来，若不是他想尽千方百计找来吃的，我们三个只怕都要被饿死了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "三个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "不错，三个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "还有一位是谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你见着他时，就会认得的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你……他在哪里？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "就在这里，只可惜你瞧不见他……我也瞧不见他。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你……你也瞧不见他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "莫非他……他是……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "他既不是怪物，也不会隐身。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "那……那为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "他就在这里，你瞧得见么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "若不是他在里面，我们又怎会去花那许多气力将船搬上来……你可知道将这半艘船搬来这里费了多少时间？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "十天？……二十天？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "一年。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_jia_xing_fa_wang",
      "text": "你去吧，该吃的时候再吃。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "直到今天，我才算真正佩服你了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "哦！是吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "我真猜不透你是用什么法子将伽星大师这样厉害的角色制住的？他居然真的如此服从你。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "世上还有我制服不住的男人么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "告诉你个好消息，今天有好东西吃。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "是不是有……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "你现在什么都不要问，等你做完了今天的早课，我自然会将一切事告诉你的，知道么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "好，我听你的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "这样才乖，我替你去弄好东西吃。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "想不到在这荒岛上也能过得这么舒服！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "舒服？纵然这里有世上一切好东西，但却有一件最坏的，世上所有的好东西也抵不过这件最坏的，你可知道那是什么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "是……是饥饿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "比饥饿更坏！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "是病痛？是寒冷？是恐惧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "这些都算不得是世上最坏的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "若说这些还不是世上最坏的事，我可真想不出天下还有什么别的事比这些事更坏的了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "告诉你，世上最最坏的就是寂寞。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "寂寞……不错。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "这些年来，每天清晨，我便将这五色锦帆升起，日落时又将它收下，为的虽然是打发这寂寞的岁月，但……但……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "但不知不觉间，你也对这五色锦帆生出了情感。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "不错。你又怎会……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你莫忘了，我老婆子虽是个无用的废物，但活了这么多年，对人情世故，多少总比别人懂得多些。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "在寂寞中，能有个通达人情世故的人聊聊天，那真比什么都好。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "只因你对那五色锦帆已生出情感，所以你才会将它保存得完整如新。这五色锦帆昔日辉煌的历史虽与你无关，但你却也总觉能有一日眼见这五色锦帆再次扬威于海上……是么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你错了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "错了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我只望有一天我能乘着这五色锦帆回家去。除了回家，我什么都不想，什么都没有放在心上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "当然是真的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "此刻若能让你回家，你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我立刻就回去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你能舍下船舱中的那个人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我……我为何舍不下他？他与我根本全无半点关系……何况，水天姬是怎么样的人，你又不是不知道。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你昔日虽然是个无情的人，心肠比铁还冷，但是经过这七年寂寞的岁月，你也有些变了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "变了？……我变不了的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你是变了，你对那没有生命的五色锦帆都会生出那么深的情感，又何况是对个活生生的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你不必骗我，更不必骗自己。你心里若没有一个很美丽的希望，又怎能忍受这七年寂寞？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我……我的希望？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你的希望，便是寄托在船舱中那个人的身上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "好孩子，你有什么心事，只管对我说吧！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我……我真不知该从何说起。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你先告诉我，船舱中那是什么人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "就是那……那大头……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "胡不愁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    }
  ],
